about.summary: Pure-Python Implementation of the AES block-cipher and common modes of operation

name: pyaes
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyaes" %}
{% set version = "1.6.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 02c1b1405c38d3c370b085fb952dd8bea3fadcee6411ad99f312cc129c536d8f

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - pyaes

about:
  home: "https://github.com/ricmoo/pyaes"
  license: "MIT"
  license_family: "MIT"
  license_file: "LICENSE.txt"
  summary: "Pure-Python Implementation of the AES block-cipher and common modes of operation"
  doc_url: "https://pypi.org/project/pyaes/"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/ricmoo/pyaes"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mwilson8
    - oblute
    - benhuff
